# Run executes exactly once

When calling **Run** (`/api/execute`), the backend must execute the pipeline **exactly one time**.

- **Never** add a fallback that re-evaluates the skrub graph (e.g. `skrub.evaluate(...)`) to populate missing node previews/details.
- If required node information can’t be produced from the single execution, **fail the run** and surface an error to the user (no retries, no second execution).

